"insert": " by anyone else, so long as derivatives are "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "also licenced under AGPL"}, {"insert": ". This ensures that "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "everyone, anywhere, can use the app freely"}, {"insert": "."}, {"attributes": {"list": "bullet"}, "insert": "\n"}, {"insert": "\nUnder these, we ensure that our app has been "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "responsibly developed"}, {"insert": ", and that it is a "}, {"attributes": {"color": "#98add9"}, "insert": "benefit to society"}, {"insert": ".\n\n"}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_5"}, "insert": "previous slide"}, {"insert": " | "}, {"attributes": {"link": "#pres_7"}, "insert": "next slide"}, {"attributes": {"align": "center"}, "insert": "\n"}]}, "text": "Ethical Considerations\n\nIt's important to consider any ethical impacts of our project, and to innovate responsibly, even if it is just an intelligent note-taking app. We evaluate these here:\n\n\n\n\nAccessibility concerns: We must ensure that the app is accessible to all, and that we are not exacerbating inequalities in access to education. In line with this, we have ensured that access needs are met, especially for users with screen readers. Further, the app is easy to install, and portable, which allows users who can only access public or shared computers to easily use the app.\n\n\n\n\nLicencing: As a group, we are commited to software being free and accessible for all, and as such have licenced the project under AGPL: The project may be freely used and modified by anyone else, so long as derivatives are also licenced under AGPL. This ensures that everyone, anywhere, can use the app freely.\n\n\n\n\nUnder these, we ensure that our app has been responsibly developed, and that it is a benefit to society.\n\n\n\n\nprevious slide | next slide", "updatedAt": 1715016507689}